caption:
my mum my forever muse. people often ask me what @bahaykubo__ means and why I chose this name for my brand. 

bahay kubo in the Philippines is a traditional home but not just any home, a simple home. It is a symbol of appreciating simplicity, modesty and working together as a community. I wanted to create a brand that embraced these values, which is why we work with @lokallab to give back to the community with every sale we make. 

for me, bahay kubo brings us back to what makes us whole—family, community, and the joy of living simply. It’s a celebration of heritage, gratitude, and a commitment to creating something meaningful and lasting.
